01:22:59,875 --> 01:23:01,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我送你們這些畜牲上西天</font></font></font>

1363
01:23:07,167 --> 01:23:08,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">芭焦扇</font></font></font>

1364
01:23:17,833 --> 01:23:19,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救我呀</font></font></font>

1365
01:23:20,708 --> 01:23:21,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真是麻煩！</font></font></font>

1366
01:23:24,208 --> 01:23:25,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師父</font></font></font>

1367
01:23:25,583 --> 01:23:27,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，救我呀！</font></font></font>

1368
01:23:36,667 --> 01:23:37,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不相信你這樣對我</font></font></font>

1369
01:23:39,625 --> 01:23:40,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師兄！</font></font></font>

1370
01:23:41,083 --> 01:23:42,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你們兩個保護師父</font></font></font>

1371
01:23:43,375 --> 01:23:44,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">知道了</font></font></font>

1372
01:23:48,250 --> 01:23:49,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞，不要呀！</font></font></font>

1373
01:23:54,417 --> 01:23:55,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你幹甚麼？</font></font></font>

1374
01:23:55,375 --> 01:23:56,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你肯過來了嗎？</font></font></font>

1375
01:23:56,375 --> 01:23:58,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">為甚麼這麼關心我，讓我死好了</font></font></font>

1376
01:24:00,125 --> 01:24:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不是關心你</font></font></font>

1377
01:24:01,375 --> 01:24:03,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只不過螻蟻都尚且偷生</font></font></font>

1378
01:24:03,292 --> 01:24:05,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神仙幹成你這個樣子乾脆不要幹算了</font></font></font>

1379
01:24:05,708 --> 01:24:07,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孫悟空，你鬥不過我的</font></font></font>

1380
01:24:28,167 --> 01:24:29,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好大條溝呀</font></font></font>

1381
01:24:31,375 --> 01:24:32,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">接住呀，快接住！</font></font></font>

1382
01:24:32,625 --> 01:24:33,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">開甚麼玩笑</font></font></font>

1383
01:24:36,250 --> 01:24:38,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我把整座城搧到太陽那邊去</font></font></font>

1384
01:24:38,458 --> 01:24:40,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我看你救得了誰？</font></font></font>

1385
01:24:53,500 --> 01:24:55,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">別妨礙我做正經事，要死你死遠點</font></font></font>

1386
01:24:56,042 --> 01:24:56,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等等！</font></font></font>

1387
01:25:03,042 --> 01:25:04,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">還騙我？</font></font></font>

1388
01:25:23,167 --> 01:25:24,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">臭猴子把城頂住</font></font></font>

1389
01:25:27,500 --> 01:25:28,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我摔！</font></font></font>

1390
01:25:30,333 --> 01:25:31,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我把你頂回去</font></font></font>

1391
01:25:42,583 --> 01:25:44,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">糟了，太熱，著火了</font></font></font>

1392
01:25:48,042 --> 01:25:48,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">混蛋！</font></font></font>

1393
01:25:49,875 --> 01:25:51,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又想怎麼樣啊？賤人</font></font></font>

1394
01:25:51,208 --> 01:25:52,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">混蛋！</font></font></font>

1395
01:25:52,292 --> 01:25:53,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你才混蛋</font></font></font>

1396
01:25:53,542 --> 01:25:54,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不是人</font></font></font>

1397
01:25:54,542 --> 01:25:55,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你才不是人</font></font></font>

1398
01:25:55,917 --> 01:25:56,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要再發瘋了</font></font></font>

1399
01:25:57,042 --> 01:25:58,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我剛才跟你說的話你明不明白？</font></font></font>

1400
01:25:58,833 --> 01:26:00,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又明不明白我已經不再是神仙呢？</font></font></font>

1401
01:26:01,833 --> 01:26:03,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我只明白一件事</font></font></font>

1402
01:26:03,167 --> 01:26:04,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">愛一個人原來是這麼痛苦</font></font></font>

1403
01:26:05,792 --> 01:26:06,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要跟我說這種廢話</font></font></font>

1404
01:26:07,583 --> 01:26:08,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我說過你認錯人啦！</font></font></font>

1405
01:26:09,750 --> 01:26:11,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那麼這串金鈴是在哪裡買的？</font></font></font>

1406
01:26:17,250 --> 01:26:18,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小心</font></font></font>

1407
01:26:22,333 --> 01:26:23,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞</font></font></font>

1408
01:26:34,208 --> 01:26:35,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小心呀師父</font></font></font>

1409
01:26:47,042 --> 01:26:47,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞</font></font></font>

1410
01:26:54,333 --> 01:26:57,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的意中人是一個蓋世英雄</font></font></font>

1411
01:26:58,708 --> 01:27:01,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有一天他會踩著七色雲彩來迎娶我</font></font></font>

1412
01:27:02,875 --> 01:27:04,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我猜中了前頭</font></font></font>

1413
01:27:06,583 --> 01:27:10,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是我猜不著這結局</font></font></font>

1414
01:27:55,750 --> 01:27:56,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師父…</font></font></font>

1415
01:27:56,792 --> 01:27:58,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要你的命！</font></font></font>

1416
01:28:37,458 --> 01:28:40,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好熱啊！我快變烤豬了</font></font></font>

1417
01:28:40,375 --> 01:28:41,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">這裡快要爆炸了</font></font></font>

1418
01:28:41,375 --> 01:28:42,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一定要靠月光寶盒才能離開這裡</font></font></font>

1419
01:28:43,708 --> 01:28:44,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走</font></font></font>

1420
01:28:47,542 --> 01:28:49,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快撞太陽，快走</font></font></font>

1421
01:28:49,542 --> 01:28:50,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帶師父先走</font></font></font>

1422
01:28:54,958 --> 01:28:55,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">青霞</font></font></font>

1423
01:28:55,958 --> 01:28:57,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我妹妹已經不在了</font></font></font>

1424
01:28:58,208 --> 01:29:00,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我看我應該回如來佛祖那兒做燈芯</font></font></font>

1425
01:29:00,667 --> 01:29:01,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你保重吧！</font></font></font>

1426
01:29:37,458 --> 01:29:39,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大師兄，這麼早就起來啦！</font></font></font>

1427
01:29:39,292 --> 01:29:40,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">發生甚麼事啊？</font></font></font>

1428
01:29:40,417 --> 01:29:42,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大師兄，你都忘記啦？</font></font></font>

1429
01:29:42,375 --> 01:29:43,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">昨晚碰上一場大風沙</font></font></font>

1430
01:29:43,833 --> 01:29:45,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你把我們帶回這裡來啦</font></font></font>

1431
01:29:46,292 --> 01:29:47,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走！</font></font></font>

1432
01:29:48,333 --> 01:29:49,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上那去師父？　﹣天竺</font></font></font>

1433
01:29:50,667 --> 01:29:52,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師父，怎麼這麼說話？</font></font></font>

1434
01:29:52,083 --> 01:29:54,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師父說話一向簡潔明瞭，走吧！</font></font></font>

1435
01:29:56,125 --> 01:29:57,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師父，別走那麼快嘛</font></font></font>

1436
01:30:00,333 --> 01:30:01,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師兄，小心呀！</font></font></font>

1437
01:30:01,833 --> 01:30:02,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">謝謝！</font></font></font>

1438
01:30:06,625 --> 01:30:08,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">相傳五百年前這裡就是水濂洞</font></font></font>

1439
01:30:08,500 --> 01:30:09,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">齊天大聖住的地方</font></font></font>

1440
01:30:09,875 --> 01:30:11,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">自從他打死牛魔王</font></font></font>

1441
01:30:11,167 --> 01:30:12,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救回唐僧之後</font></font></font>

1442
01:30:12,083 --> 01:30:12,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">這個世界再沒有妖怪了</font></font></font>

1443
01:30:13,042 --> 01:30:15,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">從此以後很多人來這混水摸魚</font></font></font>

1444
01:30:15,125 --> 01:30:16,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那個傢伙</font></font></font>

1445
01:30:16,208 --> 01:30:18,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">裝個豬頭居然說自己是豬八戒</font></font></font>

1446
01:30:19,167 --> 01:30:20,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">嘩，大哥呀</font></font></font>

1447
01:30:20,542 --> 01:30:22,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你化這個裝就說自己是孫悟空啊？</font></font></font>

1448
01:30:22,625 --> 01:30:24,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">給點專業精神好不好？</font></font></font>

1449
01:30:24,583 --> 01:30:26,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看，那些毛通通都開叉了</font></font></font>

1450
01:30:26,792 --> 01:30:29,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">頭上像戴了兩塊年糕是的</font></font></font>

1451
01:30:29,125 --> 01:30:31,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出來混飯吃得花點本錢嘛</font></font></font>

1452
01:30:31,792 --> 01:30:32,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看甚麼看？</font></font></font>

1453
01:30:32,792 --> 01:30:33,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的裝是噁心嘛</font></font></font>

1454
01:30:34,042 --> 01:30:35,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">生我氣我也這麼說</font></font></font>

1455
01:30:35,667 --> 01:30:36,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不會生氣的</font></font></font>

1456
01:30:37,083 --> 01:30:38,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再給我三刀吧！</font></font></font>

1457
01:30:38,667 --> 01:30:40,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以為我不敢啊，你這混蛋</font></font></font>

1458
01:30:41,042 --> 01:30:42,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">多謝</font></font></font>

1459
01:30:43,583 --> 01:30:46,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他為什麼要我給他三刀</font></font></font>

1460
01:30:50,333 --> 01:30:51,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大師兄</font></font></font>

1461
01:30:51,333 --> 01:30:52,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">師兄啊，準備出發了</font></font></font>

1462
01:30:56,750 --> 01:30:57,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩提洞</font></font></font>

1463
01:31:00,042 --> 01:31:03,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好的…謝謝！</font></font></font>

1464
01:31:05,833 --> 01:31:07,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">謝謝…</font></font></font>

1465
01:31:09,250 --> 01:31:11,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大師兄啊，你在看甚麼？</font></font></font>

1466
01:31:11,750 --> 01:31:12,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">八戒，賣豆腐那兩個</font></font></font>

1467
01:31:12,917 --> 01:31:14,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哪兩個？</font></font></font>

1468
01:31:14,167 --> 01:31:16,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">豆腐西施嘛</font></font></font>

1469
01:31:16,708 --> 01:31:17,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">聽這裡的人說</font></font></font>

1470
01:31:17,792 --> 01:31:18,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她們辛辛苦苦賣豆腐</font></font></font>

1471
01:31:18,958 --> 01:31:19,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">賺到錢</font></font></font>

1472
01:31:19,958 --> 01:31:22,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是給她們相公上京考狀元的</font></font></font>

1473
01:31:26,667 --> 01:31:28,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">狀元到</font></font></font>

1474
01:31:37,625 --> 01:31:39,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎呀，媚娘啊媚娘</font></font></font>

1475
01:31:39,542 --> 01:31:41,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真是恭喜你啊！恭喜你們</font></font></font>

1476
01:31:41,167 --> 01:31:43,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你們相公高中狀元了</font></font></font>

1477
01:31:43,375 --> 01:31:45,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">還不趕快去迎接他？</font></font></font>

1478
01:31:47,417 --> 01:31:48,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">娘子！</font></font></font>

1479
01:31:50,625 --> 01:31:52,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">相公　﹣娘子</font></font></font>

1480
01:31:55,958 --> 01:31:57,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走開吧！三八你看甚麼？</font></font></font>

1481
01:31:59,625 --> 01:32:01,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">娘子，啊</font></font></font>

1482
01:32:03,208 --> 01:32:05,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">辛苦娘子磨豆腐</font></font></font>

1483
01:32:05,750 --> 01:32:08,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">辛苦娘子磨豆腐啊</font></font></font>

